{"tid":454235,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[紐約恐襲]貨車鏟上單車徑撞人 至少8死十幾傷","createTime":"2017-11-01T02:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T05:30:11.000Z","uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4ec23bb93715fc6e8232f8b84feeccdc4e5d9227","tid":454235,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:55:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171101/57402163\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171101%2F57402163&d=6F8V%2FcmdKJwXYAFZaRuzKbZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=ce0ea170\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171101%2F57402163&h=65ec597d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171101/57402163</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">美國紐約下曼哈頓區周二下午發生貨車鏟上單車徑撞人襲擊，至少8死十幾傷。疑兇下車後展示疑似槍物體，高呼「真主偉大」，被警員開槍制服</span>。市長白思豪指事件是恐怖襲擊。聯邦調查局介入調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，事發於西區公路附近，鄰近是一間高中和世貿中心遺址。紐約市警方在Twitter表示，涉事小型貨車撞單車客和行人後，在當地名校斯泰弗森特高中（Stuyvesant High School）外與一部校巴相撞，疑兇下車展示兩把仿真槍，警員向他開槍，之後制服他。警方指校巴上兩名兒童和兩名成年人受傷。<br />\n比利時外相表示，一名比利時國民在襲擊中罹難。<br />\n那部有Home Depot標誌的貨車損毀，單車徑上遍佈單車殘骸。有目擊者見到貨車全速駛入單車徑，撞到多人。有屍體倒臥高中外。22歲學生威廉斯表示聽到5響槍聲，見到一名身材魁梧的鬈髮男子被捕，他表現平靜，無反抗。<br />\n警方指<span style=\"color: red;\">疑兇是29歲男子賽波夫（Sayfullo Saipov），2010年由烏茲別克來到美國，持有綠卡，住在新澤西州</span>，持有佛羅里達州車牌。行兇時手持彩彈槍和氣槍，被警員擊中腹部，已被送院。<br />\n白宮表示，總統特朗普已獲知會這次襲擊，指兇徒是喪心病狂。<br />\n<br />\n路透社／美國《紐約郵報》／《紐約每日新聞》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7363baed7690be3ec08b2464adaecca93c5e3be","tid":454235,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:02:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d6662fecbdea88072ee8bbb9edbb75a3ad2fa7f","tid":454235,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:17:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07a180fd34c6c8d9bb12f5f79c98717b87a9521","tid":454235,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:21:10.000Z","msg":"屌那星，揸車撞鳩人呢d真係毫無預計，避都避唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f63d1d00a5a8a74dcb6a8d531f97bd8637a7f7","tid":454235,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:02:07.000Z","msg":"支持全面禁用貨車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d608acf400b259f22091cf7c820cd09ee2a1d7","tid":454235,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:06:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌那星，揸車撞鳩人呢d真係毫無預計，避都避唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n武器都唔洗買"},{"pid":"177afb6d008a7bc8851400e92abe52bd6c1788f7","tid":454235,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:30:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}